[
    {
        "text": "Many people ask me, \"Mr. Duncan what is the best way to speak English?\"",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 5507,
        "slowStartTime": 0,
        "slowEndTime": 8486
    },
    {
        "text": "Is it with an American accent or a British accent?",
        "startTime": 6100,
        "endTime": 10179,
        "slowStartTime": 9081,
        "slowEndTime": 15493
    },
    {
        "text": "I think this is a very interesting question indeed.",
        "startTime": 11097,
        "endTime": 14429,
        "slowStartTime": 16796,
        "slowEndTime": 21869
    },
    {
        "text": "But my answer to this question is quite simple.",
        "startTime": 15183,
        "endTime": 17558,
        "slowStartTime": 22924,
        "slowEndTime": 26562
    },
    {
        "text": "You use the English that you feel the most comfortable with.",
        "startTime": 18259,
        "endTime": 22145,
        "slowStartTime": 27539,
        "slowEndTime": 33442
    },
    {
        "text": "You don't have to sound like an American when you're speaking.",
        "startTime": 22843,
        "endTime": 26309,
        "slowStartTime": 34415,
        "slowEndTime": 39688
    },
    {
        "text": "You don't have to sound like a British person when you're speaking.",
        "startTime": 26673,
        "endTime": 29555,
        "slowStartTime": 39859,
        "slowEndTime": 44558
    },
    {
        "text": "As long as you feel comfortable with the way you use English.",
        "startTime": 29907,
        "endTime": 33337,
        "slowStartTime": 45011,
        "slowEndTime": 50231
    },
    {
        "text": "That is the most important thing of all.",
        "startTime": 33840,
        "endTime": 36071,
        "slowStartTime": 50610,
        "slowEndTime": 54332
    },
    {
        "text": "Of course, it's also important that the other person understands what you're saying as well.",
        "startTime": 36414,
        "endTime": 41683,
        "slowStartTime": 54771,
        "slowEndTime": 62750
    },
    {
        "text": "So don't worry too much about sounding like somebody else.",
        "startTime": 42086,
        "endTime": 47252,
        "slowStartTime": 63279,
        "slowEndTime": 71103
    },
    {
        "text": "Don't try to copy somebody else's way of speaking.",
        "startTime": 47761,
        "endTime": 50745,
        "slowStartTime": 71492,
        "slowEndTime": 76342
    },
    {
        "text": "What you have to do is develop your own way of using English.",
        "startTime": 51198,
        "endTime": 54780,
        "slowStartTime": 76947,
        "slowEndTime": 82395
    },
    {
        "text": "Don't forget English is an emotional language, it's a personal language.",
        "startTime": 55031,
